snippet.title: FPV Freerider Recharged
snippet.description:
FPV Quadcopter Simulator
https://fpv-freerider.itch.io/fpv-freerider-recharged

Also available at:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/813530/FPV_Freerider_Recharged/

There is also a version for Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Freeride.FreeriderRecharged

(The music in this video is one of my favorites songs from the classic skate movie Molecules of Motion. For the longest time I was unable to find out who the artist is, thanks to a friendly person here on youtube I learned that it is 'Masquerade' by Incomplete Monday. If you are the author/owner of the song and wish that I don't use it, please let me know).
